"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:18:"featured-wordpress";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:35:"https://community.1and1.com/?p=9650";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:723:"<p>39% of all online shops are using WooCommerce already. And with good reason: WooCommerce and WordPress enable you to build powerful and modern online shops and flexible eCommerce websites. WooCommerce combines usability with excellent expandability and perfect WordPress integration. The support by Automattic &#8211; the people behind WordPress &#8211; makes WooCommerce a future-proof platform with reliable long-term support. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/start-ecommerce-website-wordpress-woocommerce/">Start your eCommerce Website with WordPress and WooCommerce</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"Philipp Bellmann";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8543:"<p><a href="https://trends.builtwith.com/shop">39% of all online shops</a> are using WooCommerce already. And with good reason:</p>\n<p><strong>WooCommerce and WordPress enable you to build powerful and modern online shops and flexible eCommerce websites. WooCommerce combines usability with excellent expandability and perfect WordPress integration.</strong></p>\n<p>The support by <a href="https://automattic.com/about/">Automattic</a> &#8211; the people behind WordPress &#8211; makes WooCommerce a future-proof platform with reliable long-term support.</p>\n<hr />\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="promo-button" href="https://my.1and1.com/APPCenter" target="_blank">Install WooCommerce</a></p>\n<h2>WooCommerce at 1&amp;1</h2>\n<p>When choosing your shop, you are committing to one system for a longer period of time. We like WooCommerce a lot, but there are <a href="https://www.1and1.com/ecommerce-website" target="_blank">alternatives</a> you might want to consider as well.</p>\n<h3>Themes you and your customers will love</h3>\n<p>WooCommerce offer professional, secure and expandable themes for your online shop, company or portfolio. Our wizard will assist you in choosing a secure theme.</p>\n<h3><img class="aligncenter wp-image-9658 size-full" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-theme-select-us-01.png" alt="Online Store: Select your Theme" width="2504" height="1346" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-theme-select-us-01.png 2504w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-theme-select-us-01-300x161.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-theme-select-us-01-768x413.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-theme-select-us-01-1024x550.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2504px) 100vw, 2504px" />Simple, international and search-engine-friendly</h3>\n<p>WooCommerce can be installed, adapted for new markets and optimized for search engines (SEO) easily in just a few steps using the 1&amp;1 WP wizard.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>WooCommerce is international: Just like WordPress, WooCommerce offers different locales for all pages and functions of your shop.</li>\n<li>WooCommerce is search-engine-friendly: The combination of WordPress and sophisticated SEO plugins puts all the tools required for effective SEO at your disposal.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>A shop your customers can trust</h3>\n<p>Your online shop is secure. WooCommerce and WordPress are checked and updated on a regular basis to prevent security holes.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Protect your online shop and your customers&#8217; data with SSL encryption.<br />\n<a href="https://community.1and1.com/activate-ssl-for-your-managed-wordpress-websites/">Activate SSL in 1&amp;1 App Center</a></li>\n<li>Combine WooCommerce with professional themes and plugins and receive a system that is extremely secure, despite its widespread distribution.</li>\n<li>Legal clarity for your market: Create legal clarity for your market with out plugin recommendations.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Great user experience, regardless of the products you sell</h3>\n<p>Selling successfully means inspiring your customer from the very start and guiding them to their goal comfortably. That is why WooCommerce employs themes with a modern and tidy interface that provides customers with an easy way to search your products and contents.</p>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9653" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/woothemes-storefront-single.gif" alt="woothemes-storefront-single" width="972" height="700" />\n<ul>\n<li>WooCommerce offers support for various business sectors.</li>\n<li>Use dynamic, animated product pages and text effects to highlight selected products.</li>\n<li>Present physical and digital products, services and memberships effectively.</li>\n<li>Offer flexible payment methods for your customers: e.g. pre-orders, subscriptions and single payments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Image: <a href="http://demo.woothemes.com/storefront/">WooCommerce Theme Demo, Storefront</a></p>\n<h3>Excellent support and documentation</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Regular updates and consistent development.</li>\n<li>The excellent <a href="https://docs.woocommerce.com/">WooCommerce documentation</a> has all the right answers to your questions and problems.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Install via 1&amp;1 App Center</h2>\n<p>The 1&amp;1 App Center now offers the option to install WordPress with <a href="https://my.1and1.com/APPCenter">WooCommerce free of charge</a>.</p>\n<h3><strong><a href="https://my.1and1.com/APPCenter" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-9657 size-full" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-type-select-us-01.png" alt="1&amp;1 App Center: Select Website Type" width="2234" height="1294" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-type-select-us-01.png 2234w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-type-select-us-01-300x174.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-type-select-us-01-768x445.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/wp-assistent-type-select-us-01-1024x593.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2234px) 100vw, 2234px" /></a></strong></h3>\n<p>Select the <strong>Online Store</strong> website type in the 1&amp;1 WP wizard after installing WordPress<strong>. </strong>Choose your<strong> WooCommerce theme </strong>and<strong> </strong>expand the range of functions as needed with our recommended <strong>plugins.</strong></p>\n<h3>Getting started with WooCommerce</h3>\n<p>Once installation is complete, the WooCommerce setup wizard will guide you through the basic settings for your online shop. Here you can easily adjust important settings for your location, products and payment methods.</p>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9654" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/woocommerce-Get-Started-2-WooCommerce-e1481538438765.png" alt="woocommerce-get-started-2-woocommerce" width="2804" height="2560" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/woocommerce-Get-Started-2-WooCommerce-e1481538438765.png 2804w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/woocommerce-Get-Started-2-WooCommerce-e1481538438765-300x274.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/woocommerce-Get-Started-2-WooCommerce-e1481538438765-768x701.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/woocommerce-Get-Started-2-WooCommerce-e1481538438765-1024x935.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2804px) 100vw, 2804px" />\n<p>When the set-up is complete, you will find two new sections in your WordPress admin menu:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>WooCommerce</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Manage <strong>Orders</strong> and <strong>Vouchers</strong></li>\n<li>Adjust <strong>Settings</strong> for your online shop.</li>\n<li>In the <strong>Reports</strong> section, you will find information on orders, customers and stock management and revenue statistics by date, category or product.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Products</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Add product</strong>: Create new products and adjust stock and shipment settings. You can set up cross- and up-selling via linked products.</li>\n<li>Create and edit <strong>Categories </strong>for your online shop. You can use categories to define the order in which your products (categories) are displayed on your website.</li>\n<li>Add <strong>Keywords</strong> and descriptions for products . Keywords will help your customers find related products and can improve recommendations.</li>\n<li>Add <strong>Properties</strong>: Properties allow you to add additional product data such as size or color and use them later in the shop&#8217;s side bar.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>More on WooCommerce</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>The <a href="https://woocommerce.com/features/">features at a glance</a> at woocommerce.com.</li>\n<li>Official <a href="https://docs.woocommerce.com/">Documentation</a>, <a href="https://woocommerce.com/my-account/">Customer service</a>, <a href="https://woocommerce.com/my-account/">Help</a> for WooCommerce.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/start-ecommerce-website-wordpress-woocommerce/">Start your eCommerce Website with WordPress and WooCommerce</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:79:"https://community.1and1.com/start-ecommerce-website-wordpress-woocommerce/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:60:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:21:"WordPress 4.7 Release";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:42:"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-7/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:50:"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-7/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 12 Dec 2016 07:38:18 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Information";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"Managed WordPress";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"WordPress";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3:"4.7";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"featured";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Release";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"vaughan";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:35:"https://community.1and1.com/?p=9638";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:613:"<p>With WordPress 4.7 „Vaughan“, a great update was released, which, in addition to many improvements, also includes the brand new theme „Twenty Seventeen“.We are already distributing the update to our managed WordPress websites. WordPress standard installations usually also receive the update automatically. If you have disabled the automatic updates for your website, you can install [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-7/">WordPress 4.7 Release</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Lucas Radke";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3575:"<p>With WordPress 4.7 „Vaughan“, a great update was released, which, in addition to many improvements, also includes the brand new theme „Twenty Seventeen“.We are already distributing the update to our managed WordPress websites. WordPress standard installations usually also receive the update automatically.</p>\n<p>If you have disabled the automatic updates for your website, you can install WordPress 4.7 directly from the WordPress admin area. To do this, select <strong>Dashboard</strong> &gt; <strong>Updates</strong> and then <strong>Update Now</strong>.</p>\n<hr />\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="promo-button" href="https://mein.1und1.de/APPCenter">Install WordPress</a> oder <a class="promo-button" href="https://my.1and1.com/AllMyApplications">Manage your Websites (1&amp;1 App Center)</a></p>\n<hr />\n<p>WordPress 4.7 Highlights:</p>\n<h3>New Standard Theme Twenty Seventeen</h3>\n<p>Twenty Seventeen surprises by the use of the new video header in combination with parallax scrolling with a dynamic appearance.</p>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9646" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/twenty-seventeen-overview.jpg" alt="twenty-seventeen-overview" width="2800" height="1800" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/twenty-seventeen-overview.jpg 2800w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/twenty-seventeen-overview-300x193.jpg 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/twenty-seventeen-overview-768x494.jpg 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/twenty-seventeen-overview-1024x658.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" />\n<h3>Video Header</h3>\n<p>A video from the media library or from YouTube can now be integrated into the header area.</p>\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-9612 size-full" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/wp-twenty-seventteen-start-video-header.png" alt="WordPress Theme Twenty Seventeen with Video Header " width="2880" height="1800" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/wp-twenty-seventteen-start-video-header.png 2880w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/wp-twenty-seventteen-start-video-header-300x188.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/wp-twenty-seventteen-start-video-header-768x480.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/wp-twenty-seventteen-start-video-header-1024x640.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2880px) 100vw, 2880px" />\n<h3>Customizer</h3>\n<p>In the customizer, special attention was paid to this update. Websites can be adjusted more quickly and easily to individual needs now.</p>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9642" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/twenty-seventeen-customize.gif" alt="twenty-seventeen-customize" width="640" height="366" />\n<h3>Editor</h3>\n<p>The arrangement of the individual elements in the toolbar has been redesigned to allow even more comfortable working.</p>\n<h3>Sample Content</h3>\n<p>For new websites, sample contents (texts and images) are displayed in the customizer for a better orientation. This will make it easier for new WordPress users to enter the theme .</p>\n<p>Of course, a whole lot of other improvements have been released, on which we will report in detail.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-7/">WordPress 4.7 Release</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:47:"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-7/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0: